    <string name="score_editing_title_info">How to modify the score?</string>
    <string name="score_editing_full_info"><![CDATA[
    To modify the score during the live stream, you need to generate a <b>link</b> before the match.<br/><br/>
    This link opens a <b>web page</b> where you can update the points of both teams in real time.<br/><br/>
    🔗 It is recommended to share the link with only one trusted person to avoid simultaneous changes.<br/><br/>
    ⚠️ Anyone with the link can change the scores, so <b>do not share it publicly</b>.
]]></string>


